<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>Kahna Gam Pel Ing Ka</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Ka thilchim loh ka lunghelna,
 Lei lungngaih khel gam nuom,
 Damlai lungngaih meipi zing hi,
 Kahna gam pel ing ka.

[V2]
 Lei lungngaih luonthi hul intin,
 Nau bang ka kah bei ina;
 Lalpa na mel muh ka ngaklah,
 Beimang maiin nuoi simlei.

[V3]
 2. Kalvari ah Lal Isu chun,
 Van gam dawngkawt a hawng;
 Va gal dawtin Aw ka thagau,
 Na kumsawt gam a lang.

[V4]
 3. Ka kahna zan thim bei intin,
 Jordan luipi gal ah;
 Guol deih ka kipahna pen te,
 Laituol lenna gamah.

[V5]
 4. Tik le thuongte ka tung deimawh,?
 Thangvan tuolnuom a chun;
 Thihna lui ka galkaih tieng leh,
 Kahna gam ngai puong ie.</lyrics>
<hymn_number>189</hymn_number>
</song>